{"tid":2131664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青山病人陳云: 香港值得給共產黨統治。","createTime":"2020-07-30T04:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T04:36:02.000Z","uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9d3c5f40eecb9dc1d558182aac9746f23fe281","tid":2131664,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"青山病人陳雲：（承上貼文）香港人比共產黨更邪惡，比大陸人更賤格。一場假瘟疫，令大家看清楚香港人的真面目。值回票價。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">由於共產黨比香港人道德比較高尚，較為懂得約束權力及姑息小民，故此香港值得給共產黨統治。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/De3UA3H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDe3UA3H.png&h=95087122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158412700472225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10158412700472225%26id%3D589657224&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=730842bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158412700472225&amp;id=589657224</a><br />\n<br />\n青山病人陳雲：七月二十一日，兩群口罩法西斯在元朗火車大戰，一些戴白布口罩，一些戴黑布口罩，互相責罵對方鳩戴口罩，布口罩不能防病毒，對不起醫護和微生物學專家。之後，兩幫人和解，各自放下藤條和雨傘，互相握手，戴上藍色外科口罩，共同支持政府的抗疫措施，拍片譴責和推撞不戴口罩的正常人。<br />\nTogether they fight their virus.<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;香港史學家陳雲紀念7-21一週年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SX2iig4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSX2iig4.png&h=e73c28ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158392485477225&amp;id=589657224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10158392485477225%26id%3D589657224&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=98ad0a7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10158392485477225&amp;id=589657224</a>"},{"pid":"7e98d2a71bcd340ef36228d101cab8e38bbb5a28","tid":2131664,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d0c14baddc861afa79dc2868f20542a8b66fff","tid":2131664,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青山国師以前好似係正苦顧問嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c0104930230144cb69a5aef3d2d53549c0b996","tid":2131664,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae73250105de76fdc26ef7bc5917122bc2a256e0","tid":2131664,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d0c14baddc861afa79dc2868f20542a8b66fff","tid":2131664,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青山国師以前好似係正苦顧問嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"根本係佢痴線得滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府都頂佢唔順，佢就諗城邦論鼓吹港獨，用人民鬥政府；港人唔撐佢，佢就鼓吹一國一制，企圖用內地政府鬥市民。報復心強，唔信科學，牆頭草，講完唔理對社會後果，不負責任，如果聽呢個痴線佬意見治港，係香港不幸"}]}